parameters.name: CreateTimeRange
parameters.description: The time range in which stories were created.

parameters.name: CustomLabels
parameters.description: The custom labels in key-value pairs.

parameters.name: FigureClusterIds
parameters.description: The IDs of the face clusters.

parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description: The maximum number of entries to return. Valid values: 1 to 100. Default value: 100.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: The pagination token that is used in the next request to retrieve a new page of results. If you do not specify this token in the next request, results are returned from the beginning.

parameters.name: Order
parameters.description:
The sort order. Valid values:

*   asc: in ascending order.
*   desc: in descending order.

parameters.name: Sort
parameters.description:
The sort field. Valid values:

*   CreateTime: sorts by story creation time.
*   StoryName: sorts by story name.
*   StoryStartTime: sorts by story start time.
*   StoryEndTime: sorts by story end time.

parameters.name: StoryEndTimeRange
parameters.description: The time range for the creation time of the last photo or video in the story.

parameters.name: StoryStartTimeRange
parameters.description: The time range for the creation time of the first photo or video in the story.

parameters.name: StorySubType
parameters.description: The subtype of the story. For a list of valid values, see [Story types and subtypes](~~2743998~~).

parameters.name: StoryType
parameters.description: The type of the story. For a list of valid values, see [Story types and subtypes](~~2743998~~).

parameters.name: WithEmptyStories
parameters.description:
Specifies whether to return empty stories. Valid values:

*   true (The default value)
*   false
